task.summary:
Cleaned up Code (halfway)
Implemented changes for the adaptive linear method to make it smarter. Cleaned up code and made the function work for arbitrary dimensions.

Optimized Performance
Changed integrate function so that it runs faster. Decreased code runtime by around 4 times.

Optimized Performance
Implemented adaptive neighborhood size based on the derivative of a candidate gamma solution.

Tester Script
Wrote tester script for 1D curves. Measures error and timing!

Tester Script
Implemented small optimization that further decreases runtime by ~20%, and fixed off by 1 error.

Distance Matrices, kd-method, testing, hierarchical coarsening
Implemented kd-tree method (still in testing phase). Wrote scripts that computed shape distance marices for MPEG-7 dataset. Wrote timing scripts. Implemented hierarchical coarsening (seems to have a few bugs, need to fix). Updated example jupyter notebook.
Hierarchy Building edits (in progress), adaptive strip_height
Hierarchy Building edits, refactored some code, small changes
Fixed uniform interpolation, prepped testing script. Wrote makeshift map-reduce algorithm to utilize 60 CPUs. Separated multilevel from reduced level elastic matching.

In progress! (version 2)
Removed elastic reduced (since it marginally works). Reworked build_hierarchy. Fixed geometric discretizatoin error bug. Nearing stable release!

In progress! (version 3)
Nearing stable release! Tweaked some values.

In progress! (version 3)
Nearing stable release! Added quick Amazon AWS script for parallel computing.
